    "editor": "code",
    "content": "The town of Ash Hollow sprung from the defeat of Igenvar, the Ash Tyrant, an ancient dragon of immense power that many worried would come to conquer the entire continent. However a group of heroes rose to confront and slay the Ash Tyrant. The Cold Iron Pact defeated Igenvar 10 years ago, and freed the populace of Alastria from his grip once and for all. Ash Hollow was founded to support the immense logistical effort of redistributing the massive hoard the Ash Tyrant had collected during his reign. Thousands of tons of gold, silver, jewels, and powerful magical artifacts were removed from the mountain that once served as the Tyrant’s lair. After the effort to haul the immense hoard was done, the once temporary residents of Ash Hollow decided to band together and make a new life for themselves. The ash tainting the land made it nearly unfarmable, until a temple to the Ram God of the Harvest, Ryventa, made a successful plea to bless the land. The ash turned to potent fertilizer and the first planted crops grew just a year prior to today. \r\n\r\nThe Ash Hollow Harvest Festival serves to commemorate the first real harvest the people successfully made.",
